    "description": "Commercial kitchen exhaust hood repair labor rates and parts cost breakdown for Los Angeles — Type I grease hoods, Type II vapor hoods, exhaust fan motor, VFD/variable frequency drive, make-up air system, fire suppression linkage and fusible links, motorized dampers, control panels, grease duct cleaning to NFPA 96 / LAFD intervals. Captive-Aire, Halton, Greenheck, Gaylord, VentMaster, Accurex, Vent-A-Hood Commercial. $120 commercial diagnostic, applied to repair.",
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "priceSpecification": { "@type": "PriceSpecification", "price": "120.00", "priceCurrency": "USD", "description": "Commercial diagnostic fee, waived with repair" } }
